                "url": "/topics/had"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355245",
        "quote": "I am extremely proud of my service with the government and my efforts to help safeguard public health and protect our country against the scourge of offensive biological warfare.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steven Hatfill",
            "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355245"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Proud",
                "url": "/topics/proud"
            },
            {
                "name": "Country",
                "url": "/topics/country"
            },
            {
                "name": "Offensive",
                "url": "/topics/offensive"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355247",
        "quote": "But I am just as appalled that my experience, knowledge, dedication and service relative to defending the United States against biological warfare has been turned against me in connection with the search for the anthrax killer.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steven Hatfill",
            "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355247"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "United",
                "url": "/topics/united"
            },
            {
                "name": "Been",
                "url": "/topics/been"
            },
            {
                "name": "Turned",
                "url": "/topics/turned"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355249",
        "quote": "Later, I went down to the Washington field office and an onsite polygraph was administered.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steven Hatfill",
            "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355249"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Office",
                "url": "/topics/office"
            },
            {
                "name": "Later",
                "url": "/topics/later"
            },
            {
                "name": "Field",
                "url": "/topics/field"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355250",
        "quote": "After reviewing the polygraph charts in private, the polygraph examiner told me that I had passed and that he believed I had nothing to do with the anthrax letters.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steven Hatfill",
            "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355250"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
