    {
        "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355260",
        "quote": "And indeed, last week, the FBI executed a search warrant on my residence. This happened one day after my attorneys had left a message on the lead FBI investigator's voice mail confirming my continued readiness to answer questions and otherwise cooperate.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steven Hatfill",
            "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355260"
