    {
        "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355265",
        "quote": "All Americans value the freedom of speech and the freedom of the press, and I believe this is essential for our continued way of life. But with this freedom comes responsibility. That responsibility has been abdicated here by some in the media and some in the government.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steven Hatfill",
            "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355265"
        },
        "topics": [
