                "name": "Having",
                "url": "/topics/having"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355267",
        "quote": "After eight months of one of the most intensive public and private investigations in American history, no one - no one - has come up with a shred of evidence that I had anything to do with the anthrax letters. I have never worked with anthrax. I know nothing about this matter.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steven Hatfill",
            "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_355267"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Evidence",
                "url": "/topics/evidence"
            },
            {
                "name": "About",
                "url": "/topics/about"
            },
            {
                "name": "Private",
                "url": "/topics/private"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_688693",
        "quote": "Whether we're at war or have been attacked, the foundation of society is that you hold to the laws in place. I used to be somebody that trusted the government. Now I really don't trust anything.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steven Hatfill",
            "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_688693"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Trust",
                "url": "/topics/trust"
            },
            {
                "name": "Laws",
                "url": "/topics/laws"
            },
            {
                "name": "Been",
                "url": "/topics/been"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_688694",
        "quote": "Is the Justice Department incapable of regulating itself? Without strong regulation, the privileges we give them to investigate us, to conduct their normal anti-crime things, can spiral out of control.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steven Hatfill",
            "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_688694"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Normal",
                "url": "/topics/normal"
            },
            {
                "name": "Give",
                "url": "/topics/give"
            },
