                "name": "Privileges",
                "url": "/topics/privileges"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_688695",
        "quote": "I learned a couple things. The government can do to you whatever they want. They can break the laws, federal laws, as they see fit... You can't turn laws on and off as you deem fit.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Steven Hatfill",
            "url": "/quotes/steven_hatfill_688695"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Learned",
